229
00:13:07,347 --> 00:13:10,646
A little doughy.

230
00:13:10,751 --> 00:13:12,878
I don't know. Maybe-Maybe it was my fault.

231
00:13:12,986 --> 00:13:16,786
Maybe I just ignored the guy.

232
00:13:18,692 --> 00:13:23,095
Wow. We're just blowing
