338
00:19:46,713 --> 00:19:48,681
So, uh, can we go now?

339
00:19:51,885 --> 00:19:53,785
Yeah.

340
00:19:56,356 --> 00:19:59,257
<i>And George Michael watched
as Maeby shared the kiss...</i>

341
00:19:59,359 --> 00:20:02,920
