a boy he almost had to kiss.</i>

342
00:20:08,168 --> 00:20:12,434
<i>But, to Maeby's surprise,
she did not enjoy kissing Steve Holt.</i>

343
00:20:12,539 --> 00:20:14,336
You smell like my mom.

344
00:20:14,441 --> 00:20:17,877
<i>Michael returned to the model home
to find his son in the kitchen.</i>

345
00:20:17,977 --> 00:20:21,242
<i>- You're home.
- Yeah. I was waiting for you.</i>

346
00:20:21,347 --> 00:20:25,147
- I thought we could make some of these.
- Sure.

347
00:20:31,057 --> 00:20:35,118
I'm sorry about what I said at the school.
